{"id":47903,"date":"2026-01-10T06:58:59","date_gmt":"2026-01-10T05:58:59","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.portugalrunning.com\/?post_type=ajde_events&#038;p=47903"},"modified":"2026-05-17T18:53:25","modified_gmt":"2026-05-17T17:53:25","slug":"corrida-fpf","status":"publish","type":"ajde_events","link":"https:\/\/www.portugalrunning.com\/eventos\/corrida-fpf\/","title":{"rendered":"Corrida FPF 2026"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<!-- Contentor Principal com T\u00edtulo -->\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; width: 100%; max-width: 1100px; margin: 20px auto;\">\n  \n  <!-- T\u00edtulo Principal -->\n  <h2 style=\"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 15px; border-left: 5px solid #006643; padding-left: 15px;\">\n    Resultados\n  <\/h2>\n\n  <!-- Bloco do Iframe -->\n  <div style=\"border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\">\n    \n    <!-- Cabe\u00e7alho de Controlo -->\n    <div style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a; padding: 15px 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px;\">\n      <div>\n        <span style=\"background: #006643; color: #fff; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;\">Classifica\u00e7\u00f5es<\/span>\n        <h3 style=\"margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.5px;\">Corrida FPF &#8211; Classifica\u00e7\u00e3o Oficial<\/h3>\n      <\/div>\n      \n      <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 10px;\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/www.corridafpf.pt\/results\/forms\/pt\/classificacao.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: #3b82f6; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; transition: all 0.2s ease; border: 1px solid #2563eb;\" rel=\"noopener\">\n           Abrir em Ecr\u00e3 Total \u2197\n        <\/a>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <!-- Zona do Iframe -->\n    <div style=\"width: 100%; height: 800px; background-color: #fff; position: relative;\">\n      <iframe \n        src=\"https:\/\/www.corridafpf.pt\/results\/forms\/pt\/classificacao.aspx\" \n        width=\"100%\" \n        height=\"100%\" \n        frameborder=\"0\"\n        style=\"display: block;\"\n        allow=\"clipboard-write\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        title=\"Classifica\u00e7\u00e3o Corrida FPF\">\n      <\/iframe>\n    <\/div>\n    \n    <!-- Rodap\u00e9 Info -->\n    <div style=\"background: #f8fafc; padding: 10px 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #64748b;\">Plataforma: <strong>Corrida FPF<\/strong><\/span>\n      <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8;\">Pesquise pelo nome ou dorsal dentro da tabela<\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>A&nbsp;<strong>Corrida FPF<\/strong>, organizada pela Federa\u00e7\u00e3o Portuguesa de Futebol, realiza-se a&nbsp;<strong>17 de maio 2026<\/strong>, com partida na Av. Pierre Coubertain &#8211; em frente \u00e0 Pra\u00e7a da Maratona e chegada na Pista de Honra do Centro Desportivo Nacional do Jamor. A iniciativa conta com a corrida de 10 km e caminhada de 4 km.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>1\u20ac de cada inscri\u00e7\u00e3o reverte para a&nbsp;<strong>Rede de Emerg\u00eancia Alimentar<\/strong>. A organiza\u00e7\u00e3o oferece um bilhete para a final da Ta\u00e7a de Portugal Feminina a cada inscrito na Corrida FPF.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":47904,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"zakra_general_container_width":0,"zakra_general_content_width":0,"zakra_general_sidebar_width":0,"zakra_sticky_header":"customizer","zakra_header_main_area":true,"zakra_site_logo_width":0,"zakra_header_top_enabled":"customizer","zakra_header_top_style"